{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753900/extras/Main_Title.png?t=1738580924\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753900/extras/1Lazy_Peasant.png?t=1738580924\" />Sire! There are countless reports of peasants and workers sleeping on the job, not producing the bare minimum for the kingdom to operate! Only your watchful eye can help them understand the importance of working, for the good of the Kingdom!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753900/extras/GIF_TKIW_Steam_Building_View.gif?t=1738580924\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753900/extras/2prosper.png?t=1738580924\" />Your people\u2019s unique\u2026 ability to do nothing while unsupervised has one advantage: you have entire control on what\u2019s produced and when:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Glance at the wheat fields, and your peasants will start harvesting.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Watch the barracks and knights will be training</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Monitor your mines and forest and workers will finally be gathering stone and wood</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your Royal Skill of balancing resource production, troop training, and magic guild is what will save our kingdom! Avert your attention to other royal matters, and production will stop. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753900/extras/3ProductionLine.png?t=1738580924\" />To restock the Royal Reserve with the rarest materials, your Majesty must order the construction of Royal production Chains. This will enable your Kingdom to thrive thanks to bigger, more upgraded buildings and experienced warriors to defend our Royal Walls!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753900/extras/Zoom_in_.gif?t=1738580924\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You also shall order to trade those resources and gather ancient magical knowledge to strengthen our Royal Defenses!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753900/extras/4Defense.png?t=1738580924\" />Unfortunately, considering the enemies lurking in the shadows surrounding your Royal Kingdom, we will need to Royally improve our defenses. We shall encourage the building of  a Royal Mage Guild and start producing spells to help you defend the Castle Royal Walls. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753900/extras/SummoningDemon.gif?t=1738580924\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Our Royal Knights and Archers will also need to be trained as well as more \u2026uncommon Royal subjects\u2026 Did I mention to thy Majesty the possibility to train Royal Flour Dragons?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Depending on your Royal wishes, playstyle and strategy, we will need to adjust our building deck. There are many ways to defend our Kingdom and Royal Experimentation is key for success!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753900/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738580924","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753900/page.bg.jpg?t=1738580924","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstat