ss=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753900/extras/SummoningDemon.gif?t=1738580924\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Our Royal Knights and Archers will also need to be trained as well as more \u2026uncommon Royal subjects\u2026 Did I mention to thy Majesty the possibility to train Royal Flour Dragons?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Depending on your Royal wishes, playstyle and strategy, we will need to adjust our building deck. There are many ways to defend our Kingdom and Royal Experimentation is key for success!</p>","developers":["Hypnohead"],"genres":[{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753900/header.jpg?t=1738580924","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257059236,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257059236/movie480.mp4?t=1727386147","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257059236/movie_max.mp4?t=1727386147"},"name":"Roguelite Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257059236/8161eb447a308df354e5375bcfb4a58bae2ff61c/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1727386147","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257059236/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1727386147","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257059236/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1727386147"}},{"highlight":false,"id":257024687,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257024687/movie480.mp4?t=1716307568","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257024687/movie_max.mp4?t=1716307568"},"name":"Announcement Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257024687/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1716307568","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/s